Luck							KEY:Luck ~ Luck								CATEGORY:Power		TYPE:Power.SpecialQuality											DESC:Each rank in this extra gives you the benefit of a rank in the Luck advantage (see Luck in the Advantages chapter). It is subject to the same limits as the Luck advantage set by the GM. Flat +1 point per rank of Luck.
