Limited Direction					KEY:Move Object ~ Limited Direction					CATEGORY:Power		TYPE:Power.SpecialQuality											DESC:You can only move objects in a particular direction or path, such as only up and down (towards and away from the ground), only directly towards or away from you (attraction and repulsion), and so forth. This is useful for "gravitic" or "magnetic" versions of the effect. -1 cost per rank.
